    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Add your <strong>diced</strong> <strong>chicken thigh</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and give it a good mix up until all the chicken is coated</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580295347362-x200.jpg",
