            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> sticky chilli chicken </strong>with the <strong>salt & pepper chips </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
